Lacewing is a cross platform networking library with a C, C++ and Javascript API.


INSTALLING
----------

On Windows, use the MSVC project file in the 'msvc' directory to build a DLL/LIB.

On Linux/BSD/OS X:

    ./configure
    make
    make install
    
Node.JS module:

    ./configure
    node-waf configure build
    node-waf install
    
    